{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c7f395d78b","title":"诺否歌","origin":"《重庆市右派言论选辑第二集》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共重庆市委宣传部办公室编印，1957年8月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1206665e88","index":0,"year":1957,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"c7f395d78b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"3d6e05a0be","name":"重庆"},{"id":"eaa9b0b7b3","name":"木曰（陈恩民）"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"cda7c0c4ac","type":"title","text":"诺否歌","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"b7de1f6111","type":"authors","text":"重庆木曰（陈恩民）","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"7581dc818a","type":"subtitle","text":"诺否歌","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"4a0803b4b6","type":"appellation","text":"[编者按：木曰真名陈恩民，男，27岁，家庭出身反动军官，学生成分，现在重庆市公安局工作。其父陈鼎六曾因制造伪币，破坏我地方金融，被判刑后病死狱中，陈恩民即因此对党不满。其“诺否歌”是用：“诺我者，名利双收人称贺”“否我者，即打入”“阴山”下“油锅”等语，来诬蔑党的领导干部为“顺我者存，逆我者亡”的封建王朝官吏。]","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"d29ab012c4","type":"paragraph","text":"服从与“反抗”，","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"cbfedcd7f0","type":"paragraph","text":"含意当何讲？","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"9357aa1713","type":"paragraph","text":"任意嫁人身，","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"8f5c13aefb","type":"paragraph","text":"啼笑皆难当！","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"b1acbcc798","type":"paragraph","text":"上云下应诺，","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"a7c086d885","type":"paragraph","text":"是福不是过：","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"08f1582898","type":"paragraph","text":"不究是与非，","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"b8a50b05d3","type":"paragraph","text":"名利双施人称贺。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"afd82458d4","type":"paragraph","text":"上云下叫否，","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"778a826be5","type":"paragraph","text":"“忤我实可恶”，","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"4fd5bab06e","type":"paragraph","text":"不问出何意，","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"54e4f6be46","type":"paragraph","text":"打入“阴山”下“油锅”","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"2c187cbbb1","type":"paragraph","text":"阴山油锅是比喻，","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"50a77af023","type":"paragraph","text":"名利更为身外物。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"a14c2fd072","type":"paragraph","text":"苟若：","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"cc3e2b8c2f","type":"paragraph","text":"无争全是诺，","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"49471a2eb9","type":"paragraph","text":"君意或满足：","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"1b4dfc8abb","type":"paragraph","text":"但是，","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"70dfcc0254","type":"paragraph","text":"人民大事业","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"70d52538c4","type":"paragraph","text":"发展抑衰落？","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"50c7906cbe","type":"paragraph","text":"试问二、三在“上”人，","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"52cad5deb6","type":"paragraph","text":"你，想过未想过！？","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"ed34c5b69b","type":"subtitle","text":"迷途的羔羊（诗）　　    木曰","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"739e03bb12","type":"paragraph","text":"[编者按：本文系借用寓言诗的形式把一般干部比喻为“白色的羔羊”，把党的领导干部比喻为“铁石铸造的心肠”的人，以此来挑拨党群关系。]","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"86252fe40f","type":"paragraph","text":"迷途的羔羊：","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"58e00e0069","type":"paragraph","text":"若干生命组成的这支白色的羔羊，","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"fb3a4dd133","type":"paragraph","text":"在这里它失去了前进的勇气，方向。","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"388cc24dc2","type":"paragraph","text":"虽然它不断的在咪咪求救，","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"30f9779eee","type":"paragraph","text":"但是，可邻的小羊啊！","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"62fb019e98","type":"paragraph","text":"凭你这股微弱的力量，","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"591aa3539c","type":"paragraph","text":"怎能打动那铁石铸造的心肠。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"0fc494f40a","type":"paragraph","text":"但是，你还得小心，","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"e115b9c8c1","type":"paragraph","text":"不要乱叫乱嚷，","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"c8c18fa696","type":"paragraph","text":"假若你吵醒了——那些对你来说是巨人的酣睡，","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"953f1cc595","type":"paragraph","text":"可哀的小生命，","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"60a668df81","type":"paragraph","text":"你都无力承当。","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"cc68a03e6d","type":"paragraph","text":"你要问我这是什么原因，","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"74378ddef8","type":"paragraph","text":"我也无言可讲。","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"8737a75f62","type":"paragraph","text":"大概因为你不是红色，","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"},{"id":"25c69132c0","type":"paragraph","text":"不引起人们兴趣，抚爱与向往。","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b"}],"page":{"id":"f2594e156b","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c7f395d78b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}